Undertale 10th Anniversary fan event recap! 🥳

Thank you to everyone that joined us 🫶! This was a lot of fun to plan and to be able to create a space for fans to celebrate together. Undertale teaches us about kindness and the strength it holds and I have never experienced a fandom space that truly encapsulates that more than this one. It was wonderful getting to talk to so many of you! This game has kept a special place in my heart for 10 years and I don’t think that will ever change. 

Thank you Toby Fox for making something so special🙏🏻

Thank you again to @district9.toronto for allowing us to host this event in your space! 

Hosted by: 
@snacck_box (IG)(Contact this account if you’re looking to have an event, panel or workshop organized!) 

Muffet: @chell - cosplayer & cosmaker 
Mettaton: @keyozee 
Toriel: @Ethereal 
Nice cream guy: @SYM 

